text: Vesyoly () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Zarevskoye Rural Settlement of Shovgenovsky District, the Republic of Adygea, Russia. The population was 249 as of 2018. There are 3 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Shovgenovsky District
title: Vesyoly, Shovgenovsky District, Republic of Adygea
